main event: An observer reported sighting a mother disc and several smaller discs over Lackland AFB, Texas in October 1968.
interesting points: The observer has submitted multiple reports regarding UFO sightings,This report is noted as the observer's fourth report,The mother disc was described as having multiple smaller discs around it,The report includes complex movements and phases of the discs, The report concludes that the sighting could be unknown phenomena or a technique used by jet pilots.
sighted object: mother disc and several smaller discs
witness description: The observer sent multiple detailed reports regarding UFO sightings.
